" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/316011e01daa4040ca88619450253fd9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Sony rides up to FromSoftware, spear in hand, ready to capture that mighty dragon.\" data-chomp-id=\"316011e01daa4040ca88619450253fd9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Sony rides up to FromSoftware, spear in hand, ready to capture that mighty dragon.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/316011e01daa4040ca88619450253fd9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: FromSoftware\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"316011e01daa4040ca88619450253fd9\" data-recommend-id=\"image://316011e01daa4040ca88619450253fd9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"Sony rides up to FromSoftware, spear in hand, ready to capture that mighty dragon.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;External link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sony-talks-buy-media-powerhouse-behind-elden-ring-sources-say-2024-11-19/\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/sony-talks-buy-media-powerhouse-behind-elden-ring-sources-say-2024-11-19/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eReuters\u003c/em\u003e is reporting\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e that Sony is in talks to buy Kadokawa Corporation, the company that owns FromSoftware, Spike Chunsoft and many other Japanese businesses. If successful, it would be a big move for Sony, gaining names as big as \u003cem\u003eElden Ring\u003c/em\u003e, \u003cem\u003eDark Souls\u003c/em\u003e, and \u003cem\u003eDanganronpa\u003c/em\u003e, and be a strike back against Microsoft’s recent major purchases. - John Walker \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/sony-fromsoftware-elden-ring-dragon-ball-zero-1851702536?_gl=1*by7tfn*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjI4Njg2My4xMi4xLjE3MzIzMDIxNjkuNTEuMC4w\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/sony-fromsoftware-elden-ring-dragon-ball-zero-1851702536?_gl=1*by7tfn*_ga*MzQzNjkwNDM2LjE2NDY2NjQ1NzQ.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjI4Njg2My4xMi4xLjE3MzIzMDIxNjkuNTEuMC4w\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404\" data-recommend-id=\"image://13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"false\" data-imagerights=\"other-license\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Image for article titled This Year\u0026amp;#39;s Game Awards Nominees Revealed, Next Year\u0026amp;#39;s RPG Avowed Is Looking Great, And More Of The Week\u0026amp;#39;s Top News\" data-chomp-id=\"13556bb4e2011ba3cc9d57819903d404\" data-